-- Four Japanese Held in China for Videotaping Military Sites, Xinhua Reports
-- B y   B e n j a m i n   P u r v i s
-- 2010-09-23T13:48:51Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-09-23/four-japanese-held-in-china-for-videotaping-military-sites-xinhua-reports.html
Four Japanese people are being
investigated in China for illegally videotaping military 
targets, the Xinhua news agency reported, without saying where
it got the information.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
